.application-received.main-content
  .container.separator
    %h1.header-blurb
      Thank you for applying for the Rails Girls London Workshop on
      = @event.dates
  .container.separator
    .content
      %h3
        Hi
        #{@registration.first_name},

      %p
        We received your application, and we will be reviewing it soon.

        %br
        You can view more details about workshop
        = link_to 'here', event_url(@event)
        or
        = link_to "http://slack.railsgirls.london/", target: :_blank do
          join us on Slack.

      %p
        %strong
          We will be sending out a confirmation email
          to successful early bird applicants on #{invites_to_be_sent_date(@event)}.
        %br

      .signature
        %p Rails Girls London team :)
        = render 'shared/mailers/social_media'


.container.separator
  = render 'shared/mailers/sponsors'

.container.separator
  %p.important-info
    Important:
    %br
    Once you receive the invitation, you are requested to confirm your participation within 7 days of receiving the invitation.
    %br
    If you can no longer make it we kindly ask you to set your status to 'not attending' so we can offer your place to the next person on the waiting list.
